Package: psmv
Type: Package
Title: The Swiss Register of Plant Protection Products as an R package
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2024-01-25
Authors@R: c(
  person("Marcel", "Mathis", role = "ctb", email = "marcel.mathis@agroscope.admin.ch"),
  person("Johannes", "Ranke", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "johannes.ranke@agroscope.admin.ch",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4371-6538")),
  person("Agroscope", role = "cph"))
Description: This package provides access to data objects extracted from
  XML versions of the Swiss Register of Plant Protection Products
  'PSMV'. Please note that this is not an official source of information
  on authorisations. The official register can be accessed at
  <https://www.psm.admin.ch/de/produkte>.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: xml2, tibble, stringr, dplyr, dm, tidyr, cli
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, here, dbplyr, vctrs, DiagrammeR,
  ggplot2, testthat (>= 3.0.0), fledge, parallel
